<p>
<note n="0512002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512002">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0512003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512003">（北）＋隋【元】</note>
<note n="0512004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512004">藏＋（法師）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0512005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512005">豆＝闍【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0512006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512006">結加＝結跏【明】下同</note>
<note n="0512007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512007">靜＝靖【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0512008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512008">諦＝庠【宋】【元】【宮】，詳【明】</note>
<note n="0512009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512009">敷＋（坐而）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0512010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512010">（即）＋問【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0512011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512011">為＋（斷）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0512012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512012">何＋（等法）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0512013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512013">也＝耶【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0512014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512014">無彼＝現無【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0512015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512015">來＋（際）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0512016" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512016">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0512017" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0512017">無＋（如來）【明】</note>
<note n="0513001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0513001">取＝最【宋】【宮】</note>
<note n="0513002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0513002">人＝仁【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0513003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0513003">者＋（不作為有無者）六字【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0513004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0513004">（可）＋不【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0513005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0513005">利＋（見）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0513006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0513006">不＋（可）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0513007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0513007">可＝何【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0513008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0513008">丘＝更【明】</note>
<note n="0514001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0514001">智＝至【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0514002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0514002">佛說文殊尸利經＝是經名聖者文殊尸利行經大乘法本竟【宋】【宮】，文殊尸利行經【元】，佛說文殊尸利行經【明】</note>
<note n="0514003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0514003">經次行＋（豆那掘多譯本）六字【宋】【宮】</note>
</p>
